data.description: End Unit nestled up against the evergreen trees. This unit is priced to sell at this LOW PRICE !  Come and choose your LVP & Carpet that YOU like. Overall in good condition but needs new floor coverings & some paint.....In the last year new furnace, A/C , Soft Water System & Dishwasher.  The club house here is amazing offering a swimming pool, Hot Tub, Sauna, Fully equipped Gym along with a large gathering room w/ Loga Fireplace, kitchen, dining room & library. Needs a little TLC but at this price :-) Text agent for showing appt.
